kai se greeklish, se periptwsi pou ta ellinika den ta deixnei

entoli metaglwttisis: g++ *.cpp

Merikes genikes paradoches tou programmatos mou:
	- I ball einai i base class
	- Oi Tennis, Basketball kai Pingpong einai oi derived classes, afou kai oi treis EINAI bales
	   Etsi, efarmozetai i ennoia tis klironomikotitas, afou oi derived classes exoun ola ta 
	   xaraktiristika tis base class.
	- I ballholder einai superclass giati xeirizetai bales, diladi tin base class
	- I main apofasizei pio paixnidi tha paixtei dioti den einai armodiotita tis ballholder.
	  I ballholder xeirizetai mono bales kai epistrefontas meso tis perissoteres_kales()
	  poiou typou bales einai perissoteres ousiastika kathorizei poio paixnidi tha paixtei, 
	  alla den einai armodiotita tis na to kathorisei. 
	-  I xrisi twn virtual synartisewn exei ylopoiithei mesw twn synartisewn hit(), rest()
	   kai get_type(), opou ekteleitai i antistoixi synartisi tis derived class anti gia 
	   ekeini tis base class
	- Otan mia mpala spasei meta apo ena xtupima h xathei, feugei apo to paixnidi,
	  enw an einai ftharmeni mporei me rest na ksanapaiksei.
	- An exw ksexasei kati, yparxei panta kai i eksetasi tis askisis!!!

